"%&%" = function(a,b) paste(a,b,sep="")
my.dir = "/Volumes/dolan-lab/hwheeler/ThePlatinumStudy/GWAS/genotypes/"
source(my.dir %&% "qqunif.r")

qq-plot function

snps2exclude <- vector()
for(i in 1:12){
  gwas <- read.table(my.dir %&% 'N88_plate_effects_maf0.01.plate' %&% i %&% '.assoc',header=T)
  print("Plate " %&% i %&% " v. the rest")
  qqunif(gwas$P,plot=TRUE)
  topsnps <- filter(gwas,P<=1e-06)
  snps2exclude <- c(snps2exclude,topsnps$SNP)
}
